==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Things will be gathered together according to category.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: wù yĭ lèi jù

===Proverb===
'''[[物]][[以]][[类聚]]'''

# [[Birds of a feather flock together]].

#: '''''[[物]][[以]][[类聚]]'''，[[人以群分]].''

===Alternate forms===
[[物以類聚]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

